SUMMARY:FULT — National Investor Call
DESCRIPTION:Reach out to your dealer to confirm timing and availability\n\n
 National investor call on Wednesday\, April 29th. Replay available by 6:00
 pm ET. Contact: fsg-dcm@psc.com\nIssuer: FULTON FINL CORP (FULT)\n\nDeal c
 ontext:\nFulton Financial Corporation is conducting fixed income investor 
 calls on April 29-30\, organized by Piper Sandler and J.P. Morgan\, ahead 
 of a potential subordinated notes offering. Subject to market conditions\,
  the holding company plans an SEC-registered offering of subordinated note
 s with expected ratings of Baa2 (Moody's) and BBB(high) (Morningstar DBRS)
 \, placing the deal firmly in Investment Grade territory. No size\, tenor\
 , or pricing details have been disclosed at this mandate stage\, with Pipe
 r Sandler coordinating logistics for the investor calls.
